$ON_NUMSSCCTR
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_NUMSSCCTR From W1ECP1
Return

$AV_NUMSSCCTR
## Action LECPAY
Call LECPAY(func TRTDIV.LECPAYSIT([M:ECP0]FCY)) From TRTDIV
If [F:TCY]SOCNUMFMT<>""
 Chgfmt [M]NUMSSCCTR(indice) With "KP:"+[F:TCY]SOCNUMFMT
Else
 Chgfmt [M]NUMSSCCTR(indice) With "-K:1X"
